      <title>以色列银行副州长在延误后批准了新任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/bank-of-israel-deputy-governor-approved-for-new-term-after-delay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡（Benjamin Netanyahu）的政府重新任命了以色列副州长安德鲁·阿比尔（Andrew Abir）的任命，这一决定是在经过数周的延误之后提出的，引起了对统治联盟对机构独立的尊重的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/bank-of-israel-deputy-governor-approved-for-new-term-after-delay</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 09:06:55 GMT</pubDate>
